TopicTitle: Can anyone recognize the music from this video?

Articles.Content: Saw this video a while ago, but never found out what the music was. Can anyone recognize it?

When there's quality music on youtube and it doesn't get identified by the copyright-detectomatic, it's usually Kevin MacLeod, who gives his stuff out free-to-use.

http://www.incompetech.com
Actually I'm looking for the exact name of the song which is ten times harder, but thanks for the help vger.

That's going to be tough to find. You should download the shazzam app. It used to be just a phone number.

If that can't find it, nothing will.

Requiem in D minor, K. 626: Agnus Dei (training)

Masaaki Ishiyama
